             sworn. - I was sent for to take the prisoner into custody; the pot was delivered to me by the former witness.</p>
               <p>(It was produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's defence. I went in, and had a pennyworth of beer; when I came out, I met a gen<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179702150085"></xptr>tlewoman, who gave me a pot, and desired me to carry it to his house: I had never been in the house before,and did not know which house it was.</p>
